FBIS3-33720 "drnes020pr_94003" FBIS-NES-94-020 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Jan 1994 SOUTH ASIA Afghanistan Planes Bomb U.S. Embassy, Diplomatic Area in Kabul LD2801183194 Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network in Persian 1730 GMT 28 Jan 94 LD2801183194 Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network Language: Persian Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Battles continue between rival forces in Afghanistan. According to reports from Kabul, fighter planes belonging to General Dostam have bombed Kabul several times in which the diplomatic Wazir Akbar Khan area, the television hill, one military base, and the American embassy were hit by bombs. [passage omitted]
